    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Micrographs of Aceria onosmae n. sp., female, as viewed under phase contrast: 1. Lateral view; 2. Ventral view; 3. Dorsal view. Scale bar = 20 Μm for 1 and 3; 10 Μm for 2." ;
